did.abstract: Collection consists of black and white glass lantern slides of Pre-Columbian arts, including architecture, sculpture, ceramics, and illuminated manuscripts from Mexico, Central America, and the Andean region of South America.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Pre-Columbian arts Lantern Slide Collection, Arts Library, Yale University

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Collection consists of black and white glass lantern slides of Pre-Columbian arts, including architecture, sculpture, ceramics, and illuminated manuscripts from Mexico, Central America, and the Andean region of South America.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: Arranged by medium. Sub-arranged by format or type, country or region, culture, and site name.
